1
00:00:23,297 --> 00:00:26,170
The line thins out to steady hum,

2
00:00:26,170 --> 00:00:30,160
as two axises become one.

3
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:31,596
Trickly tiny runnel,

4
00:00:31,596 --> 00:00:33,031
warped into a tunnel.

5
00:00:33,031 --> 00:00:35,984
Steady as she goes,

6
00:00:35,984 --> 00:00:39,335
Where it leads,

7
00:00:39,335 --> 00:00:43,453
nobody knows.

8
00:00:43,802 --> 00:00:46,914
What is it, this funny feeling -

9
00:00:46,914 --> 00:00:49,786
ominous onto it's reeling.

10
00:00:49,786 --> 00:00:52,899
steady over the stepping stone.

11
00:00:52,899 --> 00:00:56,090
Seems like someone is there,

12
00:00:56,090 --> 00:00:59,091
certainly I am not alone.

13
00:00:59,441 --> 00:01:02,393
Peel of the dark, frame by frame,

14
00:01:02,393 --> 00:01:05,105
Little guardian angel speaks my name.

15
00:01:05,105 --> 00:01:06,144
Troubled trembling soul at rest,

16
00:01:06,144 --> 00:01:10,611
You have come home now,

17
00:01:10,611 --> 00:01:12,206
You did your very best.

18
00:01:12,206 --> 00:01:15,956
Say - Do you, not recognize my face?

19
00:01:15,956 --> 00:01:19,069
After all, do you not know this place?

20
00:01:19,069 --> 00:01:22,260
Welcome, we have been up waiting

21
00:01:22,260 --> 00:01:25,980
welcome home from your hibernating.

22
00:01:26,329 --> 00:01:27,605
confused and not terribly amused,

23
00:01:27,605 --> 00:01:33,989
I think perhaps, I could get used.

24
00:01:33,989 --> 00:01:42,846
to a warm welcome such as this.

25
00:01:42,846 --> 00:01:47,043
In this place, such boundless bliss.

26
00:01:47,394 --> 00:01:50,186
Even the sun here seems to radiate joy,

27
00:01:50,186 --> 00:01:53,456
What was it again you said Tolstoy?

28
00:01:53,456 --> 00:01:54,653
Iljitjs thought his thoughts

29
00:01:54,653 --> 00:01:56,329
in silent making.

30
00:01:56,329 --> 00:01:58,165
Slow textures render,

31
00:01:58,165 --> 00:01:59,489
hardly baking.

32
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,718
What, what?

33
00:02:00,718 --> 00:02:02,951
Where.. was I just before?

34
00:02:02,951 --> 00:02:04,628
Was there not a door?

35
00:02:04,628 --> 00:02:06,063
What is the matter with me,

36
00:02:06,063 --> 00:02:07,739
How did I come to be..

37
00:02:07,739 --> 00:02:41,617
here..

38
00:02:41,967 --> 00:02:44,760
Certainly I have seen this place,

39
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:48,431
I know it better then my own face.

40
00:02:48,431 --> 00:02:52,500
Something I have always known,

41
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:55,293
How could I forget my home.
